        "timestamp": "2019-07-05 09:25:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(10 comments)\n\nIn the new commit, following comments are included.\n1. Use local value instead of get/setUrl\n2. Add getkeyFromUrl()\n3. Change the logic and check if the key in Url not found in property, then throw exception.\n4. Add Url syntax check in parameter.\n5. Improve error msg in exception.\n\nSome other comments:\n1. replace() should be enough for replacing all the key in Url(not the first)\n2. AtomicReference<String> is used since in Lambda we can only use final variable\n\nNot finished yet:\nThe unit test cases are not updated fully in restclient path.\nStill need some more effort.",
        "patchset_number": 3
